|  |         ✨✨✨            |  |  Selamat Datang        |  |
|  |      Ilustrasi Medis      |  |  Kembali! 👋           |  |
|  |     Atau Pola Abstrak     |  |                        |  |
|  |        Premium (SVG)      |  |  [Email        ]       |  |
|  |                           |  |  [Kata Sandi O ]       |  |
|  |                           |  |                        |  |
|  |                           |  |  [ Lupa Sandi? ]       |  |
|  |                           |  |  [   MASUK     ]       |  |
|  |                           |  |                        |  |
